429
00:35:15,258 --> 00:35:16,802
Shin.

430
00:35:17,776 --> 00:35:19,601
Jangan ikuti aku.

431
00:35:32,929 --> 00:35:37,199
Kau mirip Oppa kalau
berpakaian seperti itu.

432
00:35:37,199 --> 00:35:40,872
Terima kasih sudah mendadak
membantu.

433
00:35:40,872 --> 00:35:43,949
Kurasa Oppa memang 
ingin bertemu Kakek.

434
00:35:44,914 --> 00:35:48,574
