501
00:41:43,117 --> 00:41:44,987
Kau ini akurat sekali.

502
00:41:46,854 --> 00:41:48,943
Hari ini, aku...

503
00:41:49,976 --> 00:41:52,737
...lihat Shin di kantor.

504
00:41:52,737 --> 00:41:56,726
Berapa banyak permintaan manusia
Nam Shin yang harus kulakukan?

505
00:41:56,726 --> 00:41:59,949
